 1 portion","carbohydrates":"8.7 g","calories":"1291 kJ \/ 311 kcal"},"usefulItems":"frying pan, large bowl, fridge, hob","hintsAndTricks":["Add a twist to these lettuce cups by swapping the pineapple for mango. Simply use <nobr>1 mango,<\/nobr> peeled and cut in <nobr>1 cm<\/nobr> cubes, instead of the pineapple.","In this delicious dish, flavourful cajun prawns combine with sweet, spicy pineapple salsa for a lighter take on traditional tacos."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","25m","4 portions"]}